  <brief_title>Pilot Study of BC-819/PEI and BCG in Patients With Superficial Transitional Cell Bladder Carcinoma</brief_title>
  <official_title>Phase I Study of BC-819/PEI and BCG in Patients With Superficial Transitional Cell Bladder Carcinoma</official_title>
